REPLACE SOURCE_FILE_PATH WITH "src/cli/cmd_help.cpp"
REPLACE HANDLER_NAME WITH "cmd_HELP"
REPLACE HAS_DIRECT_HANDLER WITH .T.
REPLACE DISPATCH_REACHABLE WITH .T.
REPLACE PUBLIC_SURFACE WITH .T.
REPLACE SELF_REGISTERED WITH .F.
REPLACE SUPPORTS_TIMER WITH .F.
REPLACE USES_OUTPUT_ROUTER WITH .T.
REPLACE USES_MESSAGE_CATALOG WITH .F.
REPLACE ACTIVE WITH .T.
REPLACE LAST_VERIFIED_AT WITH "2026-05-04"
REPLACE NOTES WITH "Seed row. HELP is the public documentation router. This memo proves SYSTEM_COMMANDS.NOTES round-trip for x64 metadata."

APPEND
REPLACE COMMAND_ID WITH "CMD_SET"
REPLACE CANONICAL_NAME WITH "SET"
