REPLACE NOTES WITH "SET is a routed command family. SET PATH, SET ORDER, SET INDEX, SET RELATION and related forms should be represented as subcommands or routed forms, not as unrelated flat commands."

APPEND
REPLACE COMMAND_ID WITH "CMD_REL"
REPLACE CANONICAL_NAME WITH "REL"
REPLACE DISPLAY_NAME WITH "REL"
